question:
ager kale, digital -> modem -> analog kora keno hoto? instead of digital ->
modem -> digital?
ans: square wave is more prune to noise. square wave er onek gula frequency 
component, shob gula pass korar moto bandwidth hoyto nai, ba ei type kono kis arki. 
high frequency componenet gula pass korar moto shamortho chilo na.